文|《财经》数据研究员徐进图|《财经》视觉中心编辑 |谢丽容1. 新增病例：国内非湖北地区下降态势坚定2月13日0—24时，全国新增确诊病例5090例，国内非湖北地区已经连续十天下降，超过两个平均潜伏期。
New cases: At 0-24: 00 on February 13, new cases were diagnosed nationwide. Non-Hubei province has fallen for 10 days in a row, exceeding the two average incubation periods.
图1图2昨天湖北发布的新增病例数因为包含了大比例的存量划转，往前、往后均不可比，所以我们沿用老口径，今天起改为新口径。
Fig. 1 Fig. 2 The number of new cases released in Hubei province yesterday is not comparable because it contains a large proportion of the total stock.
图3按老口径判断，湖北非武汉地区新增病例趋势平稳，利用新口径判断变动趋势，仍需要几天观察。
Fig. 3 According to the old caliber, the trend of new cases is stable in Hubei non-Wuhan area.
图4按老口径看，武汉新增病例也趋势平稳，按新口径仍待观察。
Fig. 4 According to the old caliber, the new cases in Wuhan also tend to be stable, according to the new calibre still to be observed.
2. 确诊病例增长率：湖北新口径增速上移，国内非湖北地区接近2%图5武汉和湖北非武汉地区新的增速均较老口径跳跃向上，变动趋势未明。
The rate of increase of confirmed cases: The new caliber of Hubei Province has increased, and the new growth rate of Wuhan and Hubei non-Wuhan areas are both higher than that of the old ones.
依老口径计算维持原来趋势。
The same trend was maintained for old-caliber calculations.
国内非湖北地区增速降至接近2%，倍增时间延长至30天以上。
Domestic non-Hubei region growth rate fell to nearly 2%, the doubling time to more than 30 days.
3.国内非湖北地区追踪力度加大，存量下降图6国内非湖北地区对密切接触者追踪力度持续加大。
The domestic non-Hubei area tracking intensity increases, the stock decline figure 6 domestic non-Hubei area to the close contact trace strength continues to increase.
图7国内非湖北地区的该项存量，随疫情缓解和排查能力提高而持续下降。
Fig. 7 The stock in non-Hubei area of China continued to decrease with the improvement of disease mitigation and detection ability.
4.新增疑似病例和疑似病例存量图8湖北和国内非湖北地区的新增疑似病例连日来连续下降。
The number of new suspected cases and suspected cases decreased for several days in Hubei and non-Hubei areas of China.
图9湖北疑似病例存量连续五日大幅下降。
Fig. 9 The stock of suspected cases in Hubei dropped for 5 consecutive days.
国内非湖北地区继续稳降。
The non-Hubei area continued to decline steadily.
5.国内非湖北地区在院治疗人数见顶图10关于现有在院治疗这个数据，需要多说几句。
5. The number of hospital admissions in non-Hubei areas of the country is shown in Figure 10.
由于不同平台发布数据不全且不尽一致，说起来可能有些烧脑。
Because different platforms publish data incompletely and inconsistently, it may be a bit of a brainstorming exercise.
湖北卫健委公布“现有在院治疗人数”，但国家卫健委并未公布现有在院治疗人数，只发布“现有确诊病例”。
Hubei Weijian committee announced "the number of people currently in hospital treatment," but the National Health Commission did not announce the number of people currently in hospital treatment, only issued "existing confirmed cases."
其逻辑关系是：“现有确诊病例”=“累计报告病例”-“累计治愈出院人数”-“累计病死人数”。
The logical relationship is: "existing confirmed cases" = "cumulative reported cases" - "cumulative number of cured discharges" - "cumulative number of cases of illness and death."
在确诊病例能够做到“尽收尽治”的情况下，我们有理由相信“现有确诊病例”=“现有在院治疗病例”。
In the case of a confirmed case, we have reason to believe that the "existing confirmed case" = "existing hospital treatment case."
所以我们一直用国家卫健委“现有确诊病例”代替“现有在院治疗人数”，并结合湖北数据计算“国内非湖北地区现有在院治疗人数”，且一直可以自洽。
So we have been using the National Health Commission "existing confirmed cases" instead of "the number of people currently in hospital," combining Hubei data to calculate "the number of people currently in hospital in non-Hubei areas of China," and has been consistent.
但昨天的数据出现异常，得出国内非湖北地区在院治疗人数出现大幅“跳增”的不合理情况。
But yesterday's data appeared abnormal, the number of people in the hospital treatment in non-Hubei region of the unreasonable situation.
经过推理（形同破案）发现，鉴于三个因素：一、湖北昨天刚刚做了大幅口径和存量调整；二、国内非湖北地区在“尽收尽治”方面比湖北好；三、这两天国内非湖北地区新出院人数和新确诊人数已在“黄金交叉点”附近，我们用2月11日国内非湖北地区在院治疗数+新增确诊数-新出院数-新死亡数，我们推算出2月12日数据，并在此基础上进一步推测有6548例确诊病例并未治愈，也并未死亡，但不在医院，而且推测他们都在湖北。
In the past two days, the number of new discharges and new confirmed cases in China's non-Hubei areas has been in the vicinity of the Golden Junction. On the basis of these two days, we extrapolated the February 12 data to estimate that 6,548 confirmed cases have not been cured or died.
我们希望，也相信他们都处在隔离状态。
We hope, and believe, that they are all in isolation.
我们暂称其为“确诊未入院病例”。
We tentatively refer to it as a "confirmed unadmitted case."
调整后数据如图10。
The adjusted data is shown in Figure 10.
可以看出湖北地区在院治疗人数仍因口径调整继续大幅增加，国内非湖北地区的这一存量已经见顶。
It can be seen that the number of hospital treatment in Hubei continued to increase significantly due to caliber adjustment, the domestic non-Hubei region of this stock has peaked.
6.新增治愈和病死率图11新增治愈数继续上升。
6. The number of new cures added to figure 11 continues to rise.
湖北新治愈人数跳升，有口径转换因素，也有存量划转因素。
Hubei new cure number jumps, has the caliber conversion factor, also has the stock transfer factor.
图12国内非湖北地区新增治愈与新增确诊人数已于2月12日成功越过“黄金交叉”点。
Fig. 12 The number of newly diagnosed and cured cases in non-Hubei areas of China successfully crossed the Golden Cross on February 12.
从这一天起，若不出大的意外，国内非湖北地区近13000例在院治疗者将开始逐步减少。
From that day on, if not major accidents, nearly 13,000 patients in non-Hubei areas of China will begin to gradually reduce.
在此之前，国内非湖北地区的另外两个重要存量“尚在接受医学观察人数”和“待排查疑似病例”皆已先后见顶下降。
Before that, the other two important stocks in non-Hubei areas of China "are still under medical observation" and "pending investigation of suspected cases" have all peaked.
由于这三大存量（我们在数说疫情0211曾详细阐述）都对应着巨大医疗资源和社会资源，它们的全面见顶下降，毫无疑问是关乎整个战局态势的“关键拐点”！图13按照新口径，湖北地区病死率明显降低，但国内非湖北地区病死率仍在缓慢提升，很多网友关心这一问题，我们在《数说疫情0212》一文中详细分析过这个问题：由于病程发展，经过一段时间后，病死率在此阶段持续小幅回升当属正常。
The overall decline of these three stocks (which we have described in detail in case 0211) corresponds to huge medical and social resources, is undoubtedly the "key inflection point" of the overall situation. Figure 13 shows that the mortality rate in Hubei region has decreased significantly, but many netizens are concerned about the problem.
因为疫情暴发初期，每日入院新增病例猛增，经过一段时间滞后，会带来死亡人数的较快增加；另一方面，随着疫情得到控制，每日新增确诊病例会出现明显下降。
Because of the surge in the number of new admissions per day in the early stages of the outbreak, there will be a relatively rapid increase in the number of deaths after a time lag; on the other hand, there will be a significant decrease in the number of newly confirmed cases per day as the outbreak is brought under control.
这一增（分子），一降（分母），一定会导致病死率回升。
This increase (molecule), a drop (denominator), will certainly lead to a rise in the death rate.
只有在疫情基本结束时，这个数值才会逼近“最终病死率”。
Only when the epidemic is largely over will this figure approach the "final fatality rate."
小结：国内非湖北地区疫情已先行见“顶”，出现“关键拐点”。
Summary: The epidemic situation in non-Hubei areas of China has seen a "peak" in advance, "key inflection point."
国内非湖北地区医疗资源供求开始由被动转主动。
The supply and demand of medical resources in non-Hubei areas began to shift from passive to active.
但湖北疫情局势仍待明朗。
But the situation in Hubei remains unclear.
还是要说：湖北加油！武汉加油！● 数说疫情数说疫情0213：今天只说湖北，武汉“堰塞湖”显形了数说疫情0212：武汉形势扭转，湖北夺回主动权，全国继续向好数说疫情0211：形势趋好，开始“测顶”数说疫情0210：武汉反弹，其他地区向好数说疫情0209：洪峰通过，见“顶”可期数说疫情0208：武汉数据反弹，治愈远超病死数说疫情0207：疫情增势继续趋缓数说疫情0206：拐点渐近▲点击图片查看更多疫情报道责编| 蒋丽 lijiang@caijing.com.cn本文为《财经》杂志原创文章，未经授权不得转载或建立镜像。
